      <div class="section-label"><span class="text-label">Contact</span></div>
      <h2 class="text-heading" style="font-size: clamp(2rem, 4vw, 3rem);">
        Let's build something<br/><span style="color: var(--accent);">together</span>
      </h2>
    </div>
    <p class="contact-desc text-body reveal reveal-delay-1">
      I enjoy connecting with people who care about building great software — 
      whether it's a collaboration, an interesting project, or just a good engineering conversation.
    </p>
    <a href="mailto:iam@mugnimaestra.dev" class="btn btn-primary contact-btn reveal reveal-delay-2">
      Say hello →
    </a>
    <div class="contact-links reveal reveal-delay-3">
      <a href="mailto:iam@mugnimaestra.dev" class="contact-link">
